    "To compare the performance of β-VAE and POD as defined in Methods, we define, following Ref.",
    "25, the energy percentage E that is captured by the low-order reconstruction as:",
    "where 〈 ⋅ 〉 indicates ensemble averaging in time, N p is the number grid points along the spatial domain u i denotes the i th reference value of fluctuating component velocity and ũi its low-order reconstruction, respectively."
